{"tid":1573470,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"消防車唔安全！消防車唔安全！消防車唔安全！","createTime":"2019-09-16T04:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T19:30:46.000Z","uid":56857,"like":567,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"69e4439148df5ea58daf71d9012a72fe8ae86155","tid":1573470,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:08:30.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 呃左大家入黎 但絕對唔係標題黨<br />\n是咁的 小弟呢幾個月黎 返工都有機會見到手足們<br />\n明白你地見到消防車 會樂意協助開路 <br />\n好感謝大家既付出<br />\n<br />\n但係大家要留意 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千萬唔好係消防車 <br />\n或其他政府車輛附近除口罩/解除裝備</span></span></strong><br />\n因為消防車/政府車輛好多cam 影住<br />\n由其係大型既消防車 係360度無死角錄影<br />\n<br />\n雖然話就話 只用作交通意外後記錄<br />\n但呢個政府 一時一樣 <br />\n唔知幾時揸住春袋 要部門交片<br />\n所以為保安全 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">切勿在政府車輛附近（包括車尾車旁） 除口罩</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n題外話：有消防（控制）既人員指出<br />\n當日有留意831 話同fire control 有一段時間無聯絡 <br />\n而其實係果段時間之前 control 同當日救護主任 係再三confirm 有10個傷者。經過42分鐘後 無啦啦少左3個人 <br />\n呢件事絕對好鬼 希望大家留意下<br />\n<br />\n文中既 <br />\n00:01分 有10名傷者 00:20仲係有10名傷者<br />\n01:02分 突然少左3個 <br />\n如果係數錯 00:01-00:20 呢19分鐘 邊有可能無發覺 <br />\n仲要係紅色傷者 遮係優先處理<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/374091\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F374091&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=e4bcbad8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/374091</a> <br />\n<br />\n最後，除左831外，新屋嶺，同近期既自殺事件<br />\n都要咬住 唔好放過 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">千萬不要成為習慣</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7cfd6985f8d1abe557826980479a7bd8ae62152","tid":1573470,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:08:52.000Z","msg":"10連"},{"pid":"b0c5e2a672bbb84e250e3fd376924e5a833b3131","tid":1573470,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:09:03.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"d33c3960132a2ff3ca21140d6b6d30c4728116e1","tid":1573470,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:09:14.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"c65e52c1ad2d406e1fa1c5de44b4df23e1b28309","tid":1573470,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:09:25.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"3461ce94323d5789c2748ddc69fe9e283cb9efba","tid":1573470,"uid":128522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你地"},{"pid":"0b145fdd803b3061958d0b17bb866942915355df","tid":1573470,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:09:37.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"481a33dacaf88beb3b4e759fddc5217122f2a454","tid":1573470,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3461ce94323d5789c2748ddc69fe9e283cb9efba","tid":1573470,"uid":128522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:10:13.000Z","msg":"錯了 <br />\n香港 多謝唔放棄既一群手足們"},{"pid":"b72d3ed0f5713553aaeceb571a26fd73f441e293","tid":1573470,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909fa8cd6d17f47c7a953727d0422df8b8a5a57c","tid":1573470,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:11:02.000Z","msg":"香港人加油"},{"pid":"218a0456f30f8f91aa6c8593875d877810bc374b","tid":1573470,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217954ee9dfea9be691c914ef909117930e86e91","tid":1573470,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy