" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/374091</a> <br />\n<br />\n最後，除左831外，新屋嶺，同近期既自殺事件<br />\n都要咬住 唔好放過 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">千萬不要成為習慣</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:05:09.000Z","msg":"知道"},{"pid":"91f862cebc1587773992db23917338112ff97759","tid":1573470,"uid":159762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:22:07.000Z","msg":"多謝提醒！各位手足安全至上<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6729607abfd920bb48d4dba719793d091377d863","tid":1573470,"uid":61191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:32:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7de1fa7915fe4cb5965980153c24a89021393578","tid":1573470,"uid":54220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"480cf91832428f9f6e066ba8e58bf6fed85ca422","tid":1573470,"uid":285924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:46:17.000Z","msg":"其實咁快讓路比消防係咪會浪費左火魔法師嘅心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ea5e296e495e81d93386f90108e6ccb37eb6a0","tid":1573470,"uid":7494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T07:05:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e8534b43fd9a558ae626f211ece8110aa0c90b42","tid":1573470,"uid":55028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09